languages.text: Отсюда кажется, что этот роскошный особняк не пострадал от взрывов, но в него не попасть. Что-то блокирует вход изнутри.

traits.locale_text: Отсюда кажется, что этот роскошный особняк не пострадал от взрывов, но в него не попасть. Что-то блокирует вход изнутри.

languages.text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

languages.text: Von deiner Position aus sieht es nicht so aus, als wäre dieses prächtige Anwesen von Explosionen beschädigt worden, aber du kannst es nicht betreten. Etwas blockiert den Zugang von innen.
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: Von deiner Position aus sieht es nicht so aus, als wäre dieses prächtige Anwesen von Explosionen beschädigt worden, aber du kannst es nicht betreten. Etwas blockiert den Zugang von innen.

languages.text: Depuis votre point de vue en hauteur, cette luxueuse demeure ne semble pas avoir été endommagée par les explosions, mais vous ne pouvez pas y pénétrer : l'entrée est bloquée de l'intérieur.
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: Depuis votre point de vue en hauteur, cette luxueuse demeure ne semble pas avoir été endommagée par les explosions, mais vous ne pouvez pas y pénétrer : l'entrée est bloquée de l'intérieur.

languages.text: 从你的视角来看，这座奢华的宅邸似乎并没有被爆炸损坏，但你却没办法进去。宅邸入口被里面的什么东西挡住了。
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: 从你的视角来看，这座奢华的宅邸似乎并没有被爆炸损坏，但你却没办法进去。宅邸入口被里面的什么东西挡住了。

languages.text: あなたの立ち位置から見たところ、この豪華な館は爆発で損傷を受けてはいないようだが、中に入ることはできない。内側から入り口を塞がれているようだ。
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: あなたの立ち位置から見たところ、この豪華な館は爆発で傷ついてはいないようだが、中に入ることはできない。何かが内側から入り口を塞いでいるようだ。

languages.text: Desde tu posición, no parece que esta lujosa mansión haya recibido daños por las explosiones, pero no puedes entrar. Algo está bloqueando la entrada desde el interior.
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: Desde tu posición, no parece que esta lujosa mansión haya recibido daños por las explosiones, pero no puedes entrar. Algo está bloqueando la entrada desde el interior.

languages.text: Bulunduğun yerden baktığında bu ihtişamlı malikâne, patlamalardan hasar almamış gibi duruyor ancak içine giremiyorsun. Kapının arkasındaki bir şey içeriye girişi engelliyor.
languages.original_text: From your vantage point, it does not seem like this lavish mansion has been damaged by explosions, but you cannot enter. Something is blocking the entrance from the inside.

traits.locale_text: Bulunduğun yerden baktığında bu ihtişamlı köşk, patlamalardan hasar almamış gibi duruyor ancak içine giremiyorsun. Kapının arkasındaki bir şey içeriye girişi engelliyor.
